Plot Synopsis:

The land of Neotopia is attacked by the Dark Axis, evil invaders from another dimension who wish to conquer this land. Neotopia's answer: the secret Super Dimensional Guard and their defenders, the Gundam Force. Led by Captain Gundam, the Gundam Force and its team of Gundams with special abilities are aided by a boy named Shute as they stop at nothing to defend the land from the Dark Axis and to defeat them once and for all.

Before someone gets on my case about the opening for the initial 26 eps not being the official opening: I know. The videos did not include the intros for either season, and the 2nd season did not have the ending either (the exception to both of these being episode 52). I can't find any record of the song "True" by Shimokawa Mikuni being used as the opening for this show: it is the opening for Dragon Drive, but I found this video (which seems to be official despite the lack of documentation) and as I can't stand the official openings (and I can't find a clip of the second one), I used this one. Also, the ending for the 1st season is the dubbed one: I can't seem to find the japanese ones except for the final ending which you see in episode 52.

I couldn't get my hands on too many of the japanese RAWs nor would I probably have been able to provide subtitles had I found them all, so the dub will have to do for now.

A big thank-you to SDFANkysbeth on You.Tube for uploading the 2nd season so I could splice the videos together.
